                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per round</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> Swiftrun's clergy swiftly strike with their daggers against each enemy in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:5], with a @Check[reflex|dc:21|basic] save. The damage dealt depends on the number of actions.</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> @Damage[(1d4+1)[piercing]] damage</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> @Damage[(2d4+7)[piercing]] damage</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span> @Damage[(2d4+10)[piercing]] damage</p>"
